00:27:03.950 --> 00:27:10.360
John Sarno's idea -- this idea that most people's
chronic pain is a symptom of some sort of

00:27:10.360 --> 00:27:15.750
distressed emotion and that just knowing that
your pain is not something wrong with your

00:27:15.750 --> 00:27:18.220
body, but that it's related to emotions and
stress.

00:27:18.220 --> 00:27:21.880
His idea is that -- just knowing that -- cures
