00:27:21.880 --> 00:27:25.960
Kind of an education process of just kind
of cognitive insight.

00:27:25.960 --> 00:27:28.610
And once you have that "aha" moment, the whole
pain changes.

00:27:28.610 --> 00:27:33.290
So, anecdotally, I know one person who says
that that's true.

00:27:33.290 --> 00:27:37.440
As someone who's very interested in the mechanisms,
I like to know a little bit more.

00:27:37.440 --> 00:27:42.020
But in terms of what might be happening in
the brain, why an emotion that you either

00:27:42.020 --> 00:27:46.200
