But I think that most of the evidence suggests

00:27:57.059 --> 00:28:03.300
that there was a physical start as well.
So it's not going to be completely random.

00:28:03.300 --> 00:28:09.880
Like, you never had a back injury or any issues
around the back, but suddenly, anger is going

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:13.130
to create back pain.
I think it's useful to think about all of

00:28:13.130 --> 00:28:18.330
us as having physical vulnerabilities that
chronic stress and emotions will latch on

00:28:18.330 --> 00:28:20.970
to.
But I like his idea that dealing with the

00:28:20.970 --> 00:28:28.760
emotions is a good place to start.
Yes. Oh, oh sorry.

