00:29:01.850 --> 00:29:06.410
A It depends. It's a great question.
When I mentioned "five modalities" -- you

00:29:06.410 --> 00:29:10.890
got to breathe, you got to meditate, relax,
exercise, take care of yourself -- that can

00:29:10.890 --> 00:29:12.900
